    "faq.q1": "How much does a photoshoot in Istanbul cost?",
    "faq.a1": "Our Istanbul photoshoot packages start from <strong>49 EUR</strong> for solo sessions. Couple sessions are 99 EUR, family sessions 129 EUR, rooftop sessions 129 EUR, and proposal sessions 149 EUR. All packages include professionally edited photos and many include a city tour experience.",
